                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4" />
                            <path d="M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="author-name">Anne Curtis</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-date">09/22/25</div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="meta-label">Category: <span class="meta-value">Disaster Risk Reduction</span></span>
                <span class="meta-label">Office: <span class="meta-value">Disaster Office (ACDRRMO)</span></span>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="proposal-title">
                    Project Recommendation: Flood Preparedness and Emergency Response Enhancement
                </h3>
                <p class="proposal-excerpt">
                    This project recommendation addresses recurring challenges related to flood evacuations,
                    emergency rescue operations, and the dissemination of typhoon advisories. During severe
                    weather events, delays in response and limited public awareness increase risks to lives and
                    property. Strengthening preparedness and communication systems is essential to minimize
                    disaster-related impacts.
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="view-more">View More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="attachments">
                <div class="attachment-thumb">
                    <div class="thumb-placeholder">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z" />
                            <polyline points="14,2 14,8 20,8" />
                            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13" />
                            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17" />
                            <polyline points="10,9 9,9 8,9" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="attachment-thumb">
                    <div class="thumb-placeholder">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z" />
